*ppc-sources-2.4 (13 Aug 2004)

  13 Aug 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> -ppc-sources-2.4.24-r4.ebuild,
  -ppc-sources-2.4.26-r1.ebuild, -ppc-sources-2.4.26-r2.ebuild,
  -ppc-sources-2.4.26-r3.ebuild, -ppc-sources-2.4.26-r4.ebuild,
  +ppc-sources-2.4.ebuild:
  Kernel 2.4 has been deprecated.

*ppc-sources-2.4.26-r4 (08 Aug 2004)

  08 Aug 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> +ppc-sources-2.4.26-r4.ebuild:
  Added fix for CAN-2004-0415.

*ppc-sources-2.4.23-r1 (17 Jul 2004)
*ppc-sources-2.4.24-r4 (17 Jul 2004)

  17 Jul 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> -ppc-sources-2.4.23-r1.ebuild:
  Removed old kernel.

*ppc-sources-2.4.26-r3 (09 Jul 2004)

  09 Jul 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> +ppc-sources-2.4.26-r3.ebuild,
  +files/ppc-sources-2.4.26.CAN-2004-0497.patch:
  Version bump for kernel attribute vulnerabilities, bug #56479.

*ppc-sources-2.4.26-r2 (26 Jun 2004)

  26 Jun 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> +ppc-sources-2.4.26-r2.ebuild,
  +files/ppc-sources-2.4.26.CAN-2004-0495.patch,
  +files/ppc-sources-2.4.26.CAN-2004-0535.patch:
  Security bump for the CAN-2004-0495 and CAN-2004-0535 vulnerabilities.

*ppc-sources-2.4.26-r1 (04 Jun 2004)

  04 Jun 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> +ppc-sources-2.4.26-r1.ebuild,
  -ppc-sources-2.4.26.ebuild, +files/ppc-sources-2.4.26.CAN-2004-0394.patch:
  Added the CAN-2004-0394 patch; bug #47881.

* ppc-sources <pvdabeel@gentoo.org>:
  ppc-sources is now the 2.4 vanilla tree + benh + pegasos.

* ppc-sources-2.4.19 <pvdabeel@gentoo.org>:
  First official PPC kernel release.
